      <h2 style="font-family:Lora,serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#0a1628;margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:2px solid #d97706;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">⚠️ Lapsed Orders — What Seteisha Needs to Do</h2>
      <p style="color:#2d3748;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:12px;">A lapsed order occurs when a customer purchases hearing aids but does not complete their pre-shipment appointment within <strong>30 calendar days</strong>. This is a manual process — GHL cannot automatically process refunds.</p>

      <div style="background:#fff7ed;border-left:4px solid #d97706;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;font-size:.92rem;color:#92400e;">
        <strong>When a lapse happens, Seteisha will receive an internal GHL notification and a task assigned to her. There are two separate steps that must both be completed — in two different places in GHL.</strong>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#fef2f2;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;">
        <p style="font-weight:700;color:#7f1d1d;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:12px;">Step 1 — Process the Refund in GHL Payments</p>
        <ol style="padding-left:18px;margin:0;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Go to <strong>GHL → Payments → Transactions</strong></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Search for the customer by name or order number</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Click the order → select <strong>Refund</strong> → process the <strong>full refund</strong></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Confirm the refund was processed successfully</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;">
        <p style="font-weight:700;color:#14532d;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:12px;">Step 2 — Mark the Task Complete in GHL Tasks</p>
        <ol style="padding-left:18px;margin:0;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Go to <strong>GHL → Tasks</strong> (left sidebar)</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Find the task: <em>"Order lapsed — manual refund required for [Customer Name]"</em></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:8px;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">Click the task → click <strong>Mark Complete</strong></li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0;color:#2d3748;font-size:.93rem;">GHL will automatically send the cancellation SMS and email to the customer</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#eff6ff;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 20px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:.9rem;color:#1e3a5f;">
        <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> These are two separate actions in two different places. Completing only Step 1 will process the refund but will NOT send the customer their cancellation message. Completing only Step 2 without refunding will trigger the cancellation message without the refund being processed. Both steps must be done in order.
      </div>

      <div style="background:#fef2f2;border-left:4px solid #dc2626;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;font-size:.92rem;color:#7f1d1d;">
        <strong>⏱️ Time-sensitive:</strong> Process the refund within <strong>24 hours</strong> of receiving the lapse notification. The customer's payment is still on hold and they are expecting a refund.
      </div>

      <div style="background:#f0fdf4;border-left:4px solid #16a34a;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;font-size:.92rem;color:#14532d;">
        <strong>💡 Pro tip:</strong> Before processing the refund, check if the customer replied to any SMS or email at any point during the 30 days. If they did, try calling them once — they may have simply forgotten to book. If you reach them and they want to proceed, the order can be reinstated with a new purchase.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="feedbackform" style="max-width:980px;margin:0 auto 28px;padding:0 20px;">
    <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:36px 32px;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.07);">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lora',serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#0a1628;margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:2px solid #b8972a;">📝 Feedback Form — Field Reference</h2>

      <p style="color:#2d3748;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:12px;">The HBS Hearing Aid Feedback Form is sent to every customer on <strong>Day 21 after delivery</strong>. It captures their satisfaction score and follow-up preference, which determines whether a review request is sent.</p>

      <div style="background:#fefce8;border-left:4px solid #b8972a;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:.92rem;color:#713f12;">
        <strong>Form Name in GHL:</strong> HBS Hearing Aid Feedback Form<br>
        <strong>Key Field:</strong> <span class="tag tag-add">overall_rating</span> — the workflow reads this to trigger the review gate<br>
        <strong>Review sent if:</strong> overall_rating = 3, 4, or 5 stars — 1 day after submission<br>
        <strong>Review blocked if:</strong> overall_rating = 1 or 2 stars — Seteisha task assigned instead
      </div>

      <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:#1a3a5c;margin:20px 0 10px;">Form Fields</h3>
      <table class="pipeline-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width:40px;">#</th>
            <th>Field Label &amp; Options</th>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Field Key</th>
            <th>Required</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;">
            <td><span class="stage-num">1</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>How would you rate your overall experience with Hearing Benefit Services?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">⭐ This is the field the workflow reads to trigger the review gate</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge owner-auto">Star Rating 1–5</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">overall_rating</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><span class="stage-num">2</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>How satisfied are you with the sound quality of your hearing aids?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Very Satisfied / Satisfied / Neutral / Unsatisfied / Very Unsatisfied</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Dropdown</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">sound_quality_rating</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><span class="stage-num">3</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>How comfortable are your hearing aids to wear?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Very Comfortable / Comfortable / Somewhat Uncomfortable / Very Uncomfortable</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Dropdown</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">comfort_rating</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><span class="stage-num">4</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>How easy was it to set up and start using your hearing aids?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Very Easy / Easy / Difficult / Very Difficult</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Dropdown</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">setup_rating</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><span class="stage-num">5</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>How would you rate your experience with our team?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Excellent / Good / Fair / Poor</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Dropdown</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">team_rating</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><span class="stage-num">6</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>Would you like a member of our team to contact you?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Yes, please contact me / No, I'm all good</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Radio Button</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">wants_followup</span></td>
            <td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:600;">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#eff6ff;">
            <td><span class="stage-num" style="background:#185fa5;">7</span></td>
            <td>
              <strong>What is the best time to reach you?</strong><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#185fa5;font-weight:600;">⚡ Conditional — only shows if Field 6 = "Yes, please contact me"</span><br>
              <span style="font-size:.8rem;color:#718096;">Morning (9am–12pm HST) / Afternoon (12pm–3pm HST) / Late Afternoon (3pm–6pm HST)</span>
            </td>
            <td><span class="owner-badge" style="background:#e8f0fb;color:#0a1628;">Dropdown</span></td>
            <td><span class="tag tag-add">best_time_to_call</span></td>
            <td style="color:#185fa5;font-weight:600;">Conditional</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:#1a3a5c;margin:24px 0 10px;">Hidden Fields (auto-filled by GHL)</h3>
      <table class="pipeline-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Field Key</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td><span class="tag tag-add">contact_id</span></td><td>Links submission to the correct contact record in GHL automatically</td></tr>
          <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td><span class="tag tag-add">first_name</span></td><td>Pre-fills so submissions are identifiable by name</td></tr>
          <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td><span class="tag tag-add">email</span></td><td>Pre-fills for contact record matching</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:#1a3a5c;margin:24px 0 10px;">Workflow Logic After Submission</h3>
      <table class="pipeline-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Condition</th><th>Action</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;">
            <td><span class="chip chip-green">overall_rating = 3, 4, or 5 ⭐</span></td>
            <td>Add <span class="tag tag-add">feedback-positive</span> &nbsp; Review request queued — fires 1 day later to Google, Facebook &amp; HBS website</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#fef2f2;">
            <td><span class="chip chip-red">overall_rating = 1 or 2 ⭐</span></td>
            <td>Add <span class="tag tag-manual">feedback-negative</span> &nbsp; Assign task to Seteisha — NO review request sent</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#eff6ff;">
            <td><span class="chip chip-blue">wants_followup = Yes</span></td>
            <td>Assign task to Seteisha with <span class="tag tag-add">best_time_to_call</span> in task notes — applies regardless of star rating</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <div style="background:#fff7ed;border-left:4px solid #d97706;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 20px;margin-top:16px;font-size:.92rem;color:#92400e;">
        ⚠️ <strong>For Seteisha:</strong> If you receive a <span class="tag tag-manual">feedback-negative</span> task, reach out within <strong>24 hours</strong> at the customer's preferred time. Resolve their concern completely before ever asking for a review.
      </div>

      <div style="background:#eff6ff;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 20px;margin-top:12px;font-size:.92rem;color:#1e3a5f;">
        💡 For the full interactive form preview and detailed GHL build instructions, see the <strong>HBS Feedback Form Portal</strong> — a separate staff portal document.
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

